     =20
     =20
     =20
        Introduction to Web Accessibility
     =20
      </h1></header>
    <aside class=3D"box box-full"><header class=3D"box-h  box-h-full"> <h2>=
 Summary </h2></header><div class=3D"box-i">

<p>When websites and web tools are properly designed and coded, people with=
 disabilities can use them. However, currently many sites and tools are dev=
eloped with accessibility barriers that make them difficult or impossible f=
or some people to use.</p>

<p>Making the web accessible benefits individuals, businesses, and society.=
 International web standards define what is needed for accessibility.</p>

</div></aside>



